import axios from "axios"; import { Tabs, Tab, Table, Container,Form,Button } from "react-bootstrap"; import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; //to use function to get information and useState to store data function Profileusers() { const [user, setuser] = useState({}); //#region to get data from DataBase NodeJs useEffect(() => { axios.get("http://localhost:4000/profile", { withCredentials: true }) .then(res => { setuser(res.data.user); console.log(res.data.user); }).catch(err => console.log(err)); }, []) //#endregion return (
Phone {user._id}
Name {user.name}

Password ************

) } export default Profileusers;
